<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> | OAT LIMITED</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Innovative solutions for modern construction challenges</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="service-grid">
          <div class="service">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Building Construction</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">"We build tomorrow's skylines."</p>
            <p>High-rise apartments, schools, hospitals, and custom housing projects using durable and sustainable materials.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Engineering Solutions</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">"Smart designs that stand the test of time."</p>
            <p>Civil, structural, and electrical engineering solutions with a focus on innovation, safety, and cost-efficiency.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Project Management</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">"From concept to creation."</p>
            <p>We oversee every phase of a project — budgeting, scheduling, execution, and handover — to ensure seamless delivery.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Green Building Consulting</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">"Inspired by nature, built for the future."</p>
            <p>Guidance on LEED-certified building, energy-efficient systems, and environmentally friendly materials.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-hammer"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Renovations & Restorations</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">"Breathing new life into aging structures."</p>
            <p>We modernize existing buildings while preserving their original charm and structure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Smart Infrastructure & IoT</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">"Engineering meets intelligence."</p>
            <p>Integrating IoT in buildings for smart lighting, security, water systems, and real-time monitoring.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-process">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Project Approach</h2>
        <div class="process-timeline">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Consultation & Planning</h3>
            <p>We begin by understanding your vision, requirements, and budget constraints to develop a comprehensive project plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>Design & Engineering</h3>
            <p>Our expert engineers and architects create detailed designs that align with your goals while ensuring structural integrity and compliance.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h3>Construction & Implementation</h3>
            <p>With precision and attention to detail, we bring the designs to life using quality materials and best construction practices.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
            <p>Rigorous testing and inspection ensure that every aspect of the project meets our high standards and industry regulations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">5</div>
            <h3>Handover & Support</h3>
            <p>We provide comprehensive documentation, training, and ongoing support to ensure the long-term success of your project.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need a Customized Solution?</h2>
        <p>Our team is ready to discuss your specific project requirements and develop tailored strategies.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Request Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>